12. TECHNICAL SPECIFICATIONS

Message Protocol Format:

EVENT_MESSAGE {  
    header: {  
        version: uint8  
        message_type: uint16  
        timestamp: uint64 (nanoseconds since epoch)  
        source_platform: uint8  
        encryption_method: uint8  
        compression_algorithm: uint8  
    }  
      
    auth_context: {  
        session_id: uuid128  
        user_id: uuid128  
        device_fingerprint: hash256  
        permission_mask: uint64  
    }  
      
    payload: {  
        event_data: encrypted_bytes  
        checksum: hash256  
        signature: ecdsa_signature  
    }  
      
    routing: {  
        destination_platforms: uint8[]  
        priority_level: uint8  
        ttl: uint32  
        retry_count: uint8  
    }  
}

Synchronization State Machine:

SYNC_STATE_MACHINE {  
    DISCONNECTED -> CONNECTION_ATTEMPT -> AUTHENTICATING ->   
    CAPABILITY_NEGOTIATION -> VECTOR_CLOCK_SYNC ->   
    MERKLE_VERIFICATION -> DELTA_CALCULATION ->   
    CONFLICT_DETECTION -> CONFLICT_RESOLUTION ->   
    DATA_TRANSFER -> INTEGRITY_VERIFICATION -> SYNCHRONIZED  
      
    Error transitions to RETRY_BACKOFF state  
    Network loss transitions to DISCONNECTED state  
}

